 while the topmost round </div><div class="t m161e x5d h2b ye04 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reaches the throne of the Infinite. Angels are constantly ascending </div><div class="t m6d1 x14 h2b y1200 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and descending this ladder of shining brightness, bearing the prayers </div><div class="t m2b3b x9a h34 y1295 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[18</div><div class="t ma7e x52 h1c y112a ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1 </div><div class="t md43 x7a h1c y1295 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
